name: Absolute Territory | Knee Socks/Thigh High - Updated and ReLoHaded
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

ABSOLUTE TERRITORY

There's this space between the top end of the kneesock and the skirt that mesmerizes many men...

In Japan, they call it Zettai ryōiki (絶対領域) or, in English, "Absolute Territory".

Laid bare, the upper side of the thigh, beautified by a skirt and over knee socks, is another testament to the beauty of the woman's body, kneesocks are another way to beautify it.

Download this LoRA and enter the Absolute Territory!

IMPORTANT INFORMATION:

One should not enter the Absolute Territory unprepared. In order to prepare yourselves, please take notes of the following trigger words and adjust their weight as you see fit:

  • kneesocks

  • multicolor kneesocks

  • bicolor kneesocks

  • bowtie kneesocks

  • knitted kneesocks

  • panda kneesocks

  • slouched socks

Check the prompts of their usage.

Additionally, make sure to keep the LoRA's weight between 0.5 and 0.7. You may go above 0.8 if you feel lucky!
